| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2687 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3504c5db-e076-5be0-9fec-55093c007ea9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
